If you go to the PathPlanner docs here, they explain how to set up their autoChooser. Essentially, you configure the holonomic as it says in the docs (it will not work if you don’t do this), import the necessary imports, then type this in RobotContainer and the chooser automatically populates with your autos. I hope this helps!

private final SendableChooser<Command> autoChooser;
autoChooser = AutoBuilder.buildAutoChooser();
SmartDashboard.putData("Auto Chooser", autoChooser);
public Command getAutonomousCommand() {
return autoChooser.getSelected(); }
